lib.nbt

Class MapSyncTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • lib.nbt.Tag
      • lib.nbt.MapSyncTag

  • public class MapSyncTag
extends Tag
    An extension of Tag used internally by NBTTree to provide a link between the tree model and the NBT data model. Not intended for direct use.
    Author:
    Kyrillos Tawadros
    See Also:
    NBTTree
